    "lat": null,
    "lon": null,
    "title": "Broadfield Park back to Little London Road.",
    "description": "We are trying to convince Laver Regeneration Limited to allow a 20m footpath to allow this to happen.",
    "image_url": "https://static.wixstatic.com/media/f2e522_877bab9bea3048b68e69105c23f73332~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_600,h_428,al_c,q_85,enc_avif,quality_auto/image.png",
    "image2_url": null,
    "link": "https://www.sheafportertrust.org/post/little-london-road-the-dead-end-riverside-walk-the-former-lavers-yard",
    "url_join": "https://www.sheafportertrust.org/contact",
    "url_landowner": "mailto:info@laverregen.com?subject=Request%20for%20a%20permissive%20path%20along%20the%20River%20Sheaf%20%E2%80%94%20Little%20London%20Road&body=Dear%20Laver%20Regeneration%20Limited%2C%0A%0AI%20am%20writing%20as%20a%20local%20resident%20to%20ask%20whether%20you%20would%20consider%20granting%20a%20permissive%20path%20across%20your%20land%20at%20the%20former%20Arnold%20Lavers%20yard%20on%20Little%20London%20Road%2C%20to%20close%20a%20short%20but%20important%20gap%20in%20the%20River%20Sheaf%20Walk.%0A%0AThe%20existing%20riverside%20walk%20currently%20ends%20at%20a%20dead%20end%20near%20Broadfield%2C%20with%20only%20around%2020%20metres%20of%20your%20land%20separating%20it%20from%20Little%20London%20Road.%20This%20small%20connection%20would%20complete%20a%20meaningful%20stretch%20of%20riverside%20route%20through%20Sheffield%2C%20providing%20a%20safe%20and%20pleasant%20walking%20link%20for%20local%20people%20and%20visitors%20alike.%0A%0AI%20understand%20that%20during%20the%20recent%20planning%20process%20for%20the%20Tekkers%20football%20centre%20(application%2023%2F01868%2FFUL)%2C%20the%20applicant%20was%20themselves%20supportive%20of%20providing%20this%20link%2C%20and%20that%20Sheffield%20City%20Council%2C%20local%20councillors%2C%20and%20community%20groups%20were%20also%20in%20favour.%20It%20is%20disappointing%20that%20such%20a%20modest%20connection%20remains%20undelivered.%0A%0AI%20appreciate%20that%20granting%20public%20access%20to%20private%20land%20is%20not%20a%20decision%20to%20take%20lightly.%20A%20permissive%20path%20agreement%20need%20not%20mean%20any%20permanent%20dedication%20of%20the%20land%20as%20public%20highway%20%E2%80%94%20it%20would%20simply%20allow%20walkers%20to%20use%20a%20defined%20route%20at%20your%20discretion%2C%20and%20could%20be%20structured%20with%20whatever%20conditions%20and%20safeguards%20you%20feel%20are%20appropriate.%0A%0AI%20hope%20you%20will%20give%20this%20request%20your%20consideration.%20A%20short%20stretch%20of%20riverside%20path%20here%20would%20make%20a%20real%20difference%20to%20the%20community%20and%20to%20Sheffield%27s%20green%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20it%20could%20be%20achieved%20with%20minimal%20impact%20on%20your%20land%20and%20operations.%0A%0AYours%20sincerely%2C%0A%5BYour%20name%5D%0A%5BYour%20address%5D%0A%5BOptional%3A%20your%20email%20%2F%20phone%5D",
